snippet.title: INANIMA | Survival Horror in Pixel Art | New Obscure Tales Project
snippet.description:
INANIMA is a classic survival horror experience with a pixel art aesthetic. 

Solve puzzles, investigate secrets, and face nightmarish creatures as you fight to keep your life and sanity safe.
